      <div class="card mb-4">
        <img src="https://pixabay.com/get/gd332fa1551c82553caa33b469802ddbb0cfcbe5da922357b2674368a1ee5613dc19fc094733aa284b5b422bef2ada60e7cb9bd954e42803bd0aa98726aaadf81_1280.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Pregnancy stages">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Essential Prenatal Nutrients</h5>
          
          <p>Proper nutrition during pregnancy supports healthy development of your baby and maintains your health throughout pregnancy.</p>
          
          <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
              <div class="ms-2 me-auto">
                <div class="fw-bold">Folate/Folic Acid</div>
                Helps prevent neural tube defects
              </div>
              <span class="badge bg-primary rounded-pill">400-800mcg daily</span>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
              <div class="ms-2 me-auto">
                <div class="fw-bold">Iron</div>
                Supports increased blood volume and prevents anemia
              </div>
              <span class="badge bg-primary rounded-pill">27mg daily</span>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
              <div class="ms-2 me-auto">
                <div class="fw-bold">Calcium</div>
                Builds baby's bones and teeth
              </div>
              <span class="badge bg-primary rounded-pill">1000mg daily</span>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
              <div class="ms-2 me-auto">
                <div class="fw-bold">Vitamin D</div>
                Helps absorb calcium and supports immune function
              </div>
              <span class="badge bg-primary rounded-pill">600 IU daily</span>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
              <div class="ms-2 me-auto">
                <div class="fw-bold">DHA (Omega-3)</div>
                Supports baby's brain and eye development
              </div>
              <span class="badge bg-primary rounded-pill">200-300mg daily</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          
          <div class="alert alert-info mt-3">
            <p class="mb-0">A prenatal vitamin is important, but should supplement, not replace, a balanced diet rich in fruits, vegetables, whole grains, lean proteins, and healthy fats.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Common Pregnancy Discomforts & Relief</h5>
          
          <div class="accordion" id="discomfortAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingNausea">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseNausea" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseNausea">
                  Morning Sickness
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseNausea" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingNausea" data-bs-parent="#discomfortAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p><strong>Relief strategies:</strong></p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Eat small, frequent meals</li>
                    <li>Try bland foods like crackers</li>
                    <li>Cold foods may be better tolerated</li>
                    <li>Stay hydrated (small sips throughout day)</li>
                    <li>Try ginger tea or candies</li>
                    <li>Acupressure wristbands</li>
                    <li>Vitamin B6 (with healthcare provider approval)</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p><strong>When to seek help:</strong> If unable to keep down fluids for 24 hours, signs of dehydration, weight loss.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingHeartburn">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseHeartburn" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseHeartburn">
                  Heartburn & Indigestion
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseHeartburn" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingHeartburn" data-bs-parent="#discomfortAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p><strong>Relief strategies:</strong></p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Eat small, frequent meals</li>
                    <li>Avoid spicy, greasy, acidic foods</li>
                    <li>Don't lie down after eating</li>
                    <li>Sleep with head elevated</li>
                    <li>Drink between meals rather than with food</li>
                    <li>Approved antacids (consult provider)</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
