                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseBackPain" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingBackPain" data-bs-parent="#discomfortAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p><strong>Relief strategies:</strong></p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Maintain good posture</li>
                    <li>Wear supportive shoes</li>
                    <li>Use maternity support belt</li>
                    <li>Apply heat/cold</li>
                    <li>Gentle prenatal yoga or stretching</li>
                    <li>Prenatal massage</li>
                    <li>Sleep with pregnancy pillow</li>
                    <li>Consider physical therapy</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
