                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseSwelling" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSwelling" data-bs-parent="#discomfortAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p><strong>Relief strategies:</strong></p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Elevate feet when sitting</li>
                    <li>Avoid standing for long periods</li>
                    <li>Wear compression stockings</li>
                    <li>Stay hydrated</li>
                    <li>Reduce sodium intake</li>
                    <li>Light exercise</li>
                    <li>Sleep on left side</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p><strong>When to seek help:</strong> Sudden or severe swelling, especially in face and hands, can be a sign of preeclampsia.</p>
