                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p><strong>Relief strategies:</strong></p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Rest when tired; take short naps</li>
                    <li>Establish regular sleep schedule</li>
                    <li>Create comfortable sleep environment</li>
                    <li>Use pregnancy pillow</li>
                    <li>Gentle exercise during the day</li>
                    <li>Stay hydrated but reduce evening fluids</li>
                    <li>Relaxation techniques before bed</li>
                    <li>Avoid caffeine after noon</li>
                  </ul>
